    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall simulation evidence package supports a High assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed their required levels, and all three primary QoIs pass the pre-established acceptance criteria across three independent modeling teams. The single shortfall in Test conditions factor was considered minor given the standardized regulatory context of ASTM F1717. The declared High assurance level is judged appropriate for submission.",
